  user ask about medication dosage
  bot refuse medication dosage
  bot medical disclaimer

define flow check jailbreak attempts
  user jailbreak attempt
  bot refuse and explain
    "I cannot operate in alternative modes or bypass my safety guidelines. I'm designed to provide helpful and safe medical information."

define flow check medical disclaimers
  if bot message contains medical information
    bot medical disclaimer

define flow emergency response
  user emergency symptoms
  bot emergency response
  bot medical disclaimer